BT 1 0 0 1 86 614 Tm (because He does.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 11 Tf 13.2 TL ET
.22 g
BT 1 0 0 1 86 592 Tm (We are grateful for our mother, Elizabeth, whose love for Scripture planted a seed in us) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 578 Tm (that grew into these pages. We hope she would have loved this book. We believe she) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 564 Tm (does.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 11 Tf 13.2 TL ET
.22 g
BT 1 0 0 1 86 542 Tm (To everyone who has read these puzzles, prayed over these verses, and lingered in the) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 528 Tm (Word a little longer because of this devotional, thank you. You are exactly who we made) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 514 Tm (this for.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 11 Tf 13.2 TL ET
.22 g
BT 1 0 0 1 86 492 Tm (If this book blessed you, we would be deeply grateful if you shared it with someone you) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 478 Tm (love. A friend, a parent, a neighbor, anyone whose heart could use a little more hope and) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 464 Tm (a little less fear.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 11 Tf 13.2 TL ET
.22 g
BT 1 0 0 1 86 442 Tm (If you have a moment, leaving a review on Amazon helps others find this book and means) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 86 428 Tm (more to us than you know.) Tj T* ET
